Text:
I initially downloaded this torrent for the Guillemots and Sufjan tracks, but I never imagined that I would fall in love with the lesser known "girl from the north country" and "fool on the hill" as a result of this well crafted playlist.  This is what TPB is all about, thankyou.

"Two of us
Flipping through a thrift store magazine
It's Indie rock'n'roll for me"
